reviews.text: Kind of private kitchen run by top chefs in HK, but located near a wet market in very local community. No extravagant decoration & certainly the focus is their dishes. Amongst the dishes I’ve tried this night, the roasted pigeon was terrific as it’s very juicy & flavorful, pig lung soup was very yummy, the chef’s specialty dish fried rice in lobster soup was top-notched. For a guy who’s not keen on desserts like me, I was very impressed with the dried tangerine skin ice cream & water melon jelly cake. Fair to say not only the chef has proper skill, the team is good at execution too.
High standard quality of food.  Tastey.

result.name: 御進私房菜

reviews.text: 食物質素好又美味, 服務也很好
食物好好，只是某位侍應生有自已的堅持。

Kind of private kitchen run by top chefs in HK, but located near a wet market in very local community. No extravagant decoration & certainly the focus is their dishes. Amongst the dishes I’ve tried this night, the roasted pigeon was terrific as it’s very juicy & flavorful, pig lung soup was very yummy, the chef’s specialty dish fried rice in lobster soup was top-notched. For a guy who’s not keen on desserts like me, I was very impressed with the dried tangerine skin ice cream & water melon jelly cake. Fair to say not only the chef has proper skill, the team is good at execution too.
御進私房菜開店以來的忠實 fans。每道菜都是悉心烹調。絕對是平民價錢，米芝蓮享受。燒乳鴿是每次必食，lunch sets 簡直抵到喊！會繼續支持。
High standard quality of food.  Tastey.
